{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Hierarchies","anchor":"Hierarchies","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Four hierarchies are proposed for all layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default (by default)"}]},{"text":": Default buttons are used for actions which are not mandatory or essential for the user.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"strong","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The Strong “call for action” on the page should be singular and prominent, limited to one per view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It should be reserved for the most critical action, such as “Next,” “Save,” “Submit,” etc."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"minimal","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Minimal buttons are commonly used for actions that are considered less crucial. They can be used independently or together with a strong button."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Negative buttons should be used sparingly to warn of a destructive action,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for example, delete or remove, typically resulting in the opening of a confirmation dialog."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A button with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative"},{"type":"text","text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), hierarchy: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\")) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative,  style: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ A loading button","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", style: .loading) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text and icon with strong hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), text: \"Validate\", hierarchy: .strong) { \/* the action to process *\/ }"]},{"text":"Styles","anchor":"Styles","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Two style are available:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default (by default)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": used in the normal usage of button. The aspect of the button changes for following states disabled, pressed, hovered or normal (i.e. enabled)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"loading"}]},{"type":"text","text":": used after button was clicked and probably data are requested before navigate to a next screen or get updated data."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Colored Surface","anchor":"Colored-Surface","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If button is placed on colored surface using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remark: Today it is not allowed to place a Negative button on a colored surface."}]}]},{"text":"Specific behavior","anchor":"Specific-behavior","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For accessibility reasons, if the system settings for reducing motion is enabled, the loading indicator does not move."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For ecodesign reasons, if the device is in low power mode, the loading indicator does not move."}]},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/48a788-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.0.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"title":"OUDSButton","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents10OUDSButtonV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}]